	<item>
		<title>My Experience at BTW25 in Bamberg</title>
		<link>http://localhost:58387/blog/btw25-conference-experience-bamberg/</link>
		<pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
		
		<guid>http://localhost:58387/blog/btw25-conference-experience-bamberg/</guid>
		<description>&lt;p&gt;I had such a pleasant time at the &lt;a href=&#34;https://btw2025.uni-bamberg.de/&#34;&gt;BTW conference&lt;/a&gt; at &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.uni-bamberg.de/en/wiai/&#34;&gt;Fakultät Wirtschaftsinformatik und Angewandte Informatik (WIAI)&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.bamberg.info/en/&#34;&gt;Bamberg&lt;/a&gt; this week. The organizers were wonderful, and kept me well caffeinated (thank you coffee bike). The lectures and workshops were such a treat for someone who is at the beginning of their research journey. Meeting so many people whose names I only saw on research papers was, as always, quite an experience. Many thanks to the organizers and the speakers. Special thanks to the &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.cs.cit.tum.de/en/dasl/tumuchdata/&#34;&gt;TUMuchData team&lt;/a&gt; for the conference scholarship. Looking forward to the next one in &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.muenchen.de/en&#34;&gt;Munich&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:58387/images/btw25/coffee-bike.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Coffee bike at the conference venue&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The conference featured an excellent coffee service, which was much appreciated during the long days of presentations and networking.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:58387/images/btw25/poster-session.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Conference hall with poster presentations&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The poster sessions were particularly valuable, allowing researchers to present their work in an interactive format and engage in detailed discussions with attendees.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:58387/images/btw25/conference-badge.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;BTW25 Conference Badge&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The BTW conference is the most important database conference in the German-speaking area, organized by the &lt;a href=&#34;https://fg-dbs.gi.de/&#34;&gt;Database and Information Systems Special Interest Group&lt;/a&gt; of the &lt;a href=&#34;https://gi.de/&#34;&gt;German Informatics Society (GI)&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:58387/images/btw25/bamberg-old-town-hall.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Bamberg&amp;rsquo;s Old Town Hall (Altes Rathaus)&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;One of the highlights of attending the conference was experiencing the beautiful city of Bamberg, a &lt;a href=&#34;https://whc.unesco.org/en/list/624/&#34;&gt;UNESCO World Heritage Site&lt;/a&gt;. The iconic &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bamberg_Rathaus&#34;&gt;Old Town Hall&lt;/a&gt; built on a bridge over the Regnitz River is one of the city&amp;rsquo;s most famous landmarks.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
	</item>
	
	<item>
		<title>Code Blocks with VSCode Theme</title>
		<link>http://localhost:58387/blog/code-blocks-with-vscode-theme/</link>
		<pubDate>Fri, 24 Mar 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
		
		<guid>http://localhost:58387/blog/code-blocks-with-vscode-theme/</guid>
		<description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;beautiful-code-blocks-with-vscode-theme&#34;&gt;Beautiful Code Blocks with VSCode Theme&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post demonstrates how to use the new VSCode-themed code blocks in your blog posts. These code blocks replicate the familiar VS Code dark theme, making your code examples more readable and visually appealing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;basic-usage&#34;&gt;Basic Usage&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To use the VSCode theme in your code blocks, use the &lt;code&gt;vscode&lt;/code&gt; shortcode:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;{{&amp;lt; vscode lang=&amp;#34;javascript&amp;#34; &amp;gt;}}
function greeting(name) {
  return `Hello, ${name}!`;
}

console.log(greeting(&amp;#39;World&amp;#39;));
{{&amp;lt; /vscode &amp;gt;}}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;This will render as:&lt;/p&gt;




&lt;pre class=&#34;vscode-theme&#34; data-language=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;greeting&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;`Hello, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;!`&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;greeting&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;World&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt; 
&lt;h2 id=&#34;with-line-numbers&#34;&gt;With Line Numbers&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can also enable line numbers for better readability, especially for longer code blocks:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;{{&amp;lt; vscode lang=&amp;#34;python&amp;#34; lineNumbers=&amp;#34;true&amp;#34; &amp;gt;}}
def fibonacci(n):
    &amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;Generate Fibonacci sequence up to n&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;
    a, b = 0, 1
    while a &amp;lt; n:
        yield a
        a, b = b, a + b

# Print the first 10 Fibonacci numbers
for num in fibonacci(100):
    print(num)
{{&amp;lt; /vscode &amp;gt;}}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;This will render as:&lt;/p&gt;




&lt;pre class=&#34;vscode-theme&#34; data-language=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;linenumber&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;linenumber&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;fibonacci&lt;/span&gt;(n):&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;linenumber&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;Generate Fibonacci sequence up to n&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;linenumber&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    a, b &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;linenumber&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; a &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; n:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;linenumber&#34;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;yield&lt;/span&gt; a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;linenumber&#34;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        a, b &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; b, a &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; b&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;linenumber&#34;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;linenumber&#34;&gt;9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# Print the first 10 Fibonacci numbers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;linenumber&#34;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; num &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; fibonacci(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;100&lt;/span&gt;):&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;linenumber&#34;&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    print(num)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;linenumber&#34;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt; 
&lt;h2 id=&#34;supported-languages&#34;&gt;Supported Languages&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The VSCode theme currently supports syntax highlighting for:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;JavaScript&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Python&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Go&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;HTML&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CSS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here&amp;rsquo;s an example with CSS:&lt;/p&gt;




&lt;pre class=&#34;vscode-theme&#34; data-language=&#34;css&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-css&#34; data-lang=&#34;css&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;container&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;display&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;flex&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;flex-direction&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;column&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;max-width&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;800&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;px&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;margin&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;card&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;background-color&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;#f8f8f8&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;border-radius&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;px&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;padding&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;px&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;margin-bottom&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;16&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;px&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;box-shadow&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;px&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;px&lt;/span&gt; rgba(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0.1&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;/* Hover effect */&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;card&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;hover&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;transform&lt;/span&gt;: translateY(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;-2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;px&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;box-shadow&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;px&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;px&lt;/span&gt; rgba(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0.15&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;transition&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;all&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0.3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;s&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;ease&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt; 
&lt;h2 id=&#34;go-example&#34;&gt;Go Example&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And here&amp;rsquo;s a Go example with line numbers:&lt;/p&gt;




